data.description: Excellent value on this 2BR townhome in the well-established Pine Tree Village community. Layout features spacious prep kitchen upon entry that’s open to a great room, suitable to arrange for your living/dining needs. Kitchen boasts plenty of counter/cabinet space, breakfast bar and closet pantry. Great room features a vaulted ceiling and clerestory window which bathes the space in light, as well as a fireplace that’s perfect to nestle around on chilly winter nights. Bedrooms are tucked off the home’s hallway. Primary bedroom features an ensuite bath w/dual sink vanity and a shower. There’s interior laundry space (closet in the hallway)- a plus! Out back, you’ll enjoy a tiled, walled patio – gives you privacy when you want to enjoy some fun in the sun. And you have both a carport AND garage – great for vehicle protection and more storage space! Overall ideal location – You’re close enough to walk to the community amenities (tennis, basketball, and a pristine, resort style community pool). You’re also only ½ mile to Red Bug Lake Rd. and a mile to SR 436, so you’ll have quick access to essential shopping and dining. Low HOA fees, too! This home needs some TLC; come bring your sense of style, and start making new memories.  Great deal!
